<h1 class="entry-title" itemprop="headline">Trump Administration Wants to Redefine the Poverty Line, Shrinking Public Aid</h1>
</div>
</div>
</header>
<div class="row featured-media-block"><figure class="featured-media" itemprop="image" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/ImageObject">
<noscript><img width="1200" height="900" src="https://truthout.org/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/2019_0620-poverty-line-1-1200x900.jpg" class="attachment-large size-large wp-post-image" alt="A pregnant mother and her child are stopped from getting food assistance by a red barrier" itemprop="url" srcset="https://truthout.org/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/2019_0620-poverty-line-1-1200x900.jpg 1200w, https://truthout.org/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/2019_0620-poverty-line-1-200x150.jpg 200w, https://truthout.org/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/2019_0620-poverty-line-1-400x300.jpg 400w, https://truthout.org/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/2019_0620-poverty-line-1-800x600.jpg 800w, https://truthout.org/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/2019_0620-poverty-line-1.jpg 2400w" sizes="(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px"></noscript><img width="1200" height="900" src="data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20viewBox='0%200%203%202'%3E%3C/svg%3E" class="attachment-large size-large wp-post-image" alt="A pregnant mother and her child are stopped from getting food assistance by a red barrier" itemprop="url" data-sizes="(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px" data-srcset="https://truthout.org/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/2019_0620-poverty-line-1-1200x900.jpg 1200w, https://truthout.org/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/2019_0620-poverty-line-1-200x150.jpg 200w, https://truthout.org/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/2019_0620-poverty-line-1-400x300.jpg 400w, https://truthout.org/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/2019_0620-poverty-line-1-800x600.jpg 800w, https://truthout.org/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/2019_0620-poverty-line-1.jpg 2400w" data-src="https://truthout.org/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/2019_0620-poverty-line-1-1200x900.jpg" loading="lazy">
<figcaption class="wp-caption-text" itemprop="caption">A government by and for plutocrats wants to define millions of people out of poverty using a statistical sleight of hand.</figcaption><figcaption class="wp-caption-credit" itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Person"><span itemprop="name"><a href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/truthout" target="_blank">Lauren Walker / Truthout</a></span></figcaption></figure></div>
