<h2 class="entry-title" itemprop="headline">
<a href="https://truthout.org/articles/cuts-to-food-stamps-will-disproportionately-harm-lgbtq-people/">Cuts to Food Stamps Will Disproportionately Harm LGBTQ People</a>
</h2>
</div>
<div class="entry-summary" itemprop="description">
<div>
<div class="entry-summary">My Black, lesbian mother depended on food stamps because her low-income wages were not enough.</div>
</div>
</div>
<div class="entry-meta">
<dl class="article__authors byline">
<dt class="meta-label">by </dt>
<dd class="author vcard" itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Person"><span itemprop="name"><a class="url fn" href="https://truthout.org/authors/tyrone-hanley/" itemprop="url" rel="author">Tyrone Hanley</a></span>, </dd>
